name: Epic Duel (V)
Text: 'Deploy on table. A Jedi''s Resilience may not be played during move phases. The Circle Is Now Complete or Vader''s Obsession may be played during any move phase to initiate an epic duel as follows: If Vader present with specified target, each player draws two destiny (if armed with a lightsaber, each destiny is +1); add ability. Loser (lowest total) is lost, losing player loses 2 Force, and winning player may retrieve 2 Force.',
